<% @box_title = "REGISTER TO VOTE" %>
<h1>Register to vote in the state of Jeffersonia</h1>
<p>
  Thank you for your interest in voter registration. The power of our democracy 
  depends on participation from citizens like you.
</p>
<p>
  To register to vote in Jeffersonia you must attest:
</p>
<ol>
  <li>You are a citizen of the United States</li>
  <li>You are a resident of Jeffersonia</li>
  <li>You are at least 18 years of age</li>
  <li>You are not currently serving a sentence or on parole for a felony conviction</li>
</ol>
<p>
  To expedite filling out your voter registration form, please have at hand the name of the county in which you live
  and your Jeffersonia driver's license number. If you do not have a Jeffersonia driver's license, you may use the
  last four digits of your Social Security Number as an identifying number. If you do not have a Social Security
  Number or do not wish to use it as an identifying number, you may elect to have the county Board of Elections for
  your county assign you an identification number, but be aware this may cause delays in the processing of your
  application.
</p>
<p>
  To register to vote you must submit an <em>original signed form</em> to the county Board of Elections for your
  county. If you live in Adams county, you may also participate in our validation and
  accountability program for voter registrations. Your form will be electronically validated and the progress of
  your registration request will be availbale to you via our website. It is not required that you participate, and
  your participation in the program will not affect the approval or rejection of your application.
</p>

<h3>Next Step:</h3>
<ol>
  <li><%= link_to 'Download the voter registration form', '#'%>
  <li>Print it out
  <li>Complete and sign the form
  <li>Mail the original signed completed form to your county Board of Elections office
</ol>

<h4>Adams County Residents:</h4>
<p>
  If you reside in Adams county, you may use our <%= link_to 'online validation and tracking',
  step1_new_registration_citizens_path %> voter registration assistant.
</p>